# Pro Value Amplification Layer — Walkthrough

## Goal
Increase upgrade conversion through visible Pro differentiation. **Frontend only, zero backend changes.**

---

## Feature 1: Pro Insight Box

A new card below the Grade/Risk/Saturation/ROI row on the Dashboard.

**Pro users** see real computed values:
- Demand Momentum (from trendVelocity + marketSaturation)
- Commercial Intent (from profitMargin + adCompetition)
- Competition Pressure (from adCompetition + marketSaturation)

**Free users** see locked placeholders (——) with `"Upgrade to unlock advanced intelligence"` CTA button.

